===Etymology===
From dialectal {{bor|en|de|Pretzel}}, a variant of standard {{m|de|Brezel}}, from {{der|en|goh|brezzila}}, from {{der|en|ML.|brachiatellum}}, diminutive of {{der|en|la|bracchium||arm}}; named for the appearance of folded arms.

