===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|culinary}} A toasted [[bread]] or [[cracker]] usually in the shape of a loose [[knot]].
# {{lb|en|by extension}} Anything that is knotted, [[twist]]ed, or [[tangle]]d.

